          <p>Yes &mdash; genuinely free, with nothing locked behind a form or an email signup. We build them as Certified ProAdvisors to be useful first; if a tool raises a question about your own books, you&rsquo;re welcome to book a free discovery call, but there&rsquo;s no obligation and no gate.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq__item">
