        <div class="faq__answer" id="kitchen-sink-b3-listing-hub-faq-a2" data-open="false">
          <p>No. Every estimate here is built from TechBrot&rsquo;s published pricing to put you in a realistic range &mdash; it is never a binding quote. A short form can&rsquo;t see your actual file. Your exact fixed fee is always confirmed in writing within 3 business days of a free discovery call, before any work begins.</p>
