          <p>From our real, published fixed-fee pricing &mdash; the same ranges shown on the <a href="/pricing/">pricing page</a> and identical everywhere on the site. We don&rsquo;t invent figures or quote competitor prices we can&rsquo;t verify. Each tool shows its own math so you can see exactly how it reached a number.</p>
